"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/679110","HM Treasury","false","2017-01-31","<p>Latest statistics on SAYE option schemes can be found at: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/save-as-you-earn-share-option-schemes" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/save-as-you-earn-share-option-schemes</a></p><p> </p><p>The 2014-15 data is not currently available.</p>","Battersea","Jane Ellison",,"2017-01-31T14:11:01.157Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/679110/answer","Biography information for Jane Ellison","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/679110/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/679110/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2017-01-26","Save as You Earn: Tax Allowances","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how many people benefitted from income tax relief through Save As You Earn in (a) 2013-14 and (b) 2014-15.","false","Biography information for Rebecca Long Bailey","Salford and Eccles","Rebecca Long Bailey","61954"
